{"tid":858333,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大阪民宿淪垃圾屋 客人列入黑名單","createTime":"2018-10-11T17:14:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-12T09:21:35.000Z","uid":66943,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"39e8f7b613e4fd37298d4384799b605e58da898f","tid":858333,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T17:14:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.modia.com.hk/2018/10/11/102566/%E5%A4%A7%E9%98%AA%E6%B0%91%E5%AE%BF%E6%B7%AA%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE%E5%B1%8B-%E5%AE%A2%E4%BA%BA%E5%88%97%E5%85%A5%E9%BB%91%E5%90%8D%E5%96%AE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.modia.com.hk%2F2018%2F10%2F11%2F102566%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2598%25AA%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%25AE%25BF%25E6%25B7%25AA%25E5%259E%2583%25E5%259C%25BE%25E5%25B1%258B-%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2588%2597%25E5%2585%25A5%25E9%25BB%2591%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%2596%25AE%2F&d=pY0agEH7gCaDRQKpRecKoQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=b2403b61\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.modia.com.hk/2018/10/11/102566/%E5%A4%A7%E9%98%AA%E6%B0%91%E5%AE%BF%E6%B7%AA%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE%E5%B1%8B-%E5%AE%A2%E4%BA%BA%E5%88%97%E5%85%A5%E9%BB%91%E5%90%8D%E5%96%AE/</a><br />\n<br />\n一名在日本大阪經營民宿的港人Kammy，近日在Facebook分享「住得很好的客人VS 住得好可怕的客人」的比較圖，當中後者更惹關注。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.modia.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/tam-696x392.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.modia.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2Ftam-696x392.jpg&h=c359b81c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(「住在大阪」Facebook專頁網頁截圖)<br />\n帖文形容該組客人離開後留下「垃圾屋」：「我家清潔去做清掃時看到都快瘋了&hellip;&hellip;全屋都是垃圾，廚房、廁所都是垃圾！用筆畫地下，碎了的眼影就掉在床上，連沙發也染色了，怎樣也清不了。」Kammy更直言以後也不接那組客人了。<br />\n<br />\n[size=4]<strong>客人不是香港或台灣人</strong>[/size=5]<br />\n網民在留言中紛紛問客人來自哪裡，Kammy回覆否認是香港人或台灣人，並透露有要求客人賠償，但對方討價還價，又指他們是做代購的：「做代購的垃圾都多，不過算沒有公德心的他們算是第一位！ 」"},{"pid":"e0ebe53d2498ea085bf5c8d7dd127cce482114ca","tid":858333,"uid":1251,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T17:16:49.000Z","msg":"唔係香港台灣但又做代購<br />\n九成支那啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e0d26031954f3e8386f44ed4b7812e7f0430d72","tid":858333,"uid":86383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T17:57:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97c5d16c886963f7f017a53adb2713d30b881fca","tid":858333,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T07:37:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4437e72da29ef343e6d54c513daab2074a0374ed","tid":858333,"uid":52459,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T09:21:35.000Z","msg":"一定係支那人"}]}